    <h1 class="title">Cybercrime in the Philippines</h1>

    <p class="author">
        <b>By: Hamoy, Kurt Tobey L. &bull; April 6, 2026</b>
    </p>

    <p class="nav-bio">
        <a href="#intro">Introduction</a> &bull;
        <a href="#landscape">Current Landscape</a> &bull;
        <a href="#common-crimes">Most Common Crimes</a> &bull;
